data.description: Loads of updates include: roof, fresh paint, flooring carpet, windows, completely remodeled kitchen-kitchen cabinets, flooring, appliances, deck plus covered lower level deck, storage unit. Completely updated, light filled town home with private backyard & serene wooded view in a fantastic location, near North Hills, Crabtree Valley Mall, short distance to downtown Raleigh. Large, bright living room fts/fireplace with custom mantle. Upper level offers 2 large bedrooms & updated bathroom. Don't miss the basement with a large bedroom suite or bonus room, updated full bathroom, and large walk in laundry room. Fr. No HOA! Hop on I-540, 440 and major highways. Call this gorgeous property home.
